1. *Poneo* je torbu sa sobom. (He brought the bag with him.)
2. Nisam siguran da li sam *poneo* novčanik. (I'm not sure if I brought my wallet.)
3. Oni su *poneli* mnogo hrane za piknik. (They brought a lot of food for the picnic.)
4. Da li ćeš mi pomoći da *poneo* ove kutije? (Will you help me carry these boxes?)
5. Pretpostavljam da nisi *poneo* kišobran, zar ne? (I suppose you didn't bring an umbrella, did you?)
6. Kada bismo znali da će biti tako hladno, *poneli* bismo topliju odeću. (If we knew it was going to be this cold, we would have brought warmer clothes.)
7. Već sam *poneo* ove knjige u biblioteku, ne mogu ih ponovo pozajmiti. (I already brought these books to the library, I can't borrow them again.)
8. Čini mi se da sam *poneo* previše stvari na odmor. (I think I brought too many things on vacation.)
9. Nije važno koliko stvari si *ponela* na putovanje, bitno je da uživaš. (It doesn't matter how many things you brought on the trip, what matters is that you enjoy yourself.)
10. Sutra ujutro moram *poneti* svoj laptop na posao. (Tomorrow morning I have to bring my laptop to work.)